descriptionNullable: The loaded data covers a wide range of information related to Brazil's medicine sales over the two Covid pandemic years (2020 and 2021). This comprehensive dataset offers insights into the medicaments sales in Brazil and, by analyzing this data, it is possible to explore trends, identify most popular medicine, and gain a deeper understanding of the medicaments and its sales in Brazil.
